Hello,
We are using On the fly path generation during autonomous, and we’re encountering a weird issue where it will go to the wrong spot, then the next spot in what is a sort of sequence, and then resume the correct sequence. Our code is here. It happened in this match, team 1391 on the blue side far from the camera. An example of the auto working is here. Let us know any ideas!
Thanks,
1391
